    <item>
      <title>挪威向富人征税引发企业强烈反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/norway-s-tax-the-rich-drive-provokes-widening-business-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威计划对该国最富有的公民采取严厉措施，这引起企业家的强烈反对，他们警告说，此举只会加剧挪威经济对石油和天然气的严重依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/norway-s-tax-the-rich-drive-provokes-widening-business-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:23:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪相关担忧缓解，印度股市重回平静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/calm-returns-to-indian-stocks-as-modi-linked-concerns-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在激烈的选举中重新掌权，缓解了人们对政策连续性的担忧，印度股市波动性指标已下降一半以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/calm-returns-to-indian-stocks-as-modi-linked-concerns-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:22:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
