    <item>
      <title>德国试图阻止或降低欧盟对中国电动汽车征收的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/germany-trying-to-prevent-or-soften-eu-tariffs-on-chinese-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国政府正在努力阻止欧盟对中国电动汽车征收的新关税生效——或者至少在无法全面停止的情况下放宽关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/germany-trying-to-prevent-or-soften-eu-tariffs-on-chinese-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 04:31:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行缺乏债券购买削减细节导致日元暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行要求投资者等到 7 月份会议后才能公布有关缩减债券购买规模的细节，这导致日元再度走软，并推迟了对日本央行下个月加息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 03:31:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元因日本央行举措而下跌，欧洲股指期货上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国和香港股市下跌的影响，亚洲股市下跌，而由于日本央行推迟就其债券购买计划做出决定，日元兑美元汇率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
